verses.text: Mamin Jehová, ol valnhej t'a in b'it to toxonton ay a wach'k'olal. D'a masanil tiempo ol valeli to yel tzaq'uelk'och tas tzala'.
Ha yab'ixal a wach'k'olal ay t'a masanil tiempo ol valeli. Ol valanpaxeli to max q'uexmaj tas tzala', icha yaj juntzanh tas ay t'a satcha’anh.
Alnac: Ay jun in trato yet' vinhaj David in checab' ix in siq'ueli, ix vak'kan in ti' t'a vinh, ix valan t'a vinh icha tik:
Ha eb' inhtilal, ol vak'nhejcanoch eb' reyal a q'uexuloc t'a masanil tiempo, xin chi.
Mamin Jehová, masanil eb' molanek' t'a satcha’anh, ol sb'itej eb' tas satub'tac tza k'ulej. Ol yalpaxel eb' to tzaq'uelk'och tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, malaj junocxo mach t'a satcha’anh syal slajb'an sb'a ed'oc. Malaj junok eb' lajan ed'oc.
Te niwan elk'och t'a skal eb' ángel. Te ay a poder t'a yichanh eb' oyanoch t'a a patic ichanh.
Mamin Jehová Yajal t'a Smasanil, ¿mach val junocxo lajan ed'oc? Masanil tas syalnhej uuj. Tzaq'uelk'och masanil tas tzala'.
Yol a k'ab' ayek' ha' mar ayic ste ovaj ha'. Ha achxo tzak'och vaan ha' ayic ste k'anh ha'.
Ha nok' nok' ay smay t'a yol ha' mar, ix ach q'ue tek'tek' t'a yib'anh nok', ix a tek'ancham nok'. Ix a saclemej eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayach yuj a poder.
Ha satcha’anh yet' sat lum tik, ic toni. Ha ach a b'onac yol yib'anhk’inal tik yet' masanil tastac ay t'ay.
Ha norte masanto sk'och t'a sur, a ach ix a b'o'o. Ha lum vitzal Tabor yet' lum vitzal Hermón, sb'itan lum t'ayach.
Ha a k'ab' te ay yip. Ha a wach' k'ab', masanil syal yuj.
Ha a despacho te tek'an yaj yuj a wach'il yet' a tojolal. Ha t'a masanil scheclajel a wach'k'olal, tzak'an elk'och tas tzala'.
Mamin Jehová, te wach' yic eb' anima tzach b'itani. Tzalajk'olalnhej yic eb' yuj a wach'k'olal.
Ha val t'ayach syak' tzalajb'oc sk'ol eb'. Yuj a tojolal tz'ik'jichaanh eb'.
D'a val yel, te niwan ipalil tzak' t'ayonh. Yuj a wach'k'olal syalnhej cuuj.
Mamin Jehová, co Columal aji. Ach co Diosal a onh israel onh tik, co Reyal ach.

Ha t'a peca', ix ach lolon t'a vayichal, ix alan t'a eb' a checab' tzach k'anab'ajan icha tik: Ix in och yet' jun soldado te tek'an, aton jun mach sik'b'ilel vuj t'a skal in chonhab', ix vak'an yopisio.
Ix ilchaj vinhaj David in checab' vuuj, a yet' vaceite yic sik'val ix in ch'oxo' to reyxo yaj vinh.
Manh ol in och vaan in kolwaj t'a vinh, yujto a in poder ol ak'an yip vinh.
Ha eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a vinh, manh ol yal-laj yoch sk'ab' eb' t'a vinh. Ha eb' sk'ulan chukal, manh ol tzak'vanlaj eb' t'a vinh.
Ol in tek'canem eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a vinh. Ol in milancham eb' schichonoch sk'ol t'a vinh.
Ayinnhej ek' yet' vinh yujto xajan vinh vuuj. Ol vak' elk'och tas svala'. Vuujnhej ol yalnhej yuj vinh.
Ol vak' nivanb'oc smacb'en vinh. Ol schael yich t'ha ha' mar Mediterráneo masanto sk'och t'ha ha' niwan Éufrates.
Ol yalan vinh t'ayin: In Mam ach, in Diosal ach, a t'ayach tzin col in b'a, xcham vinh.
Ha inxo ol vak' snivanil yelk'och vinh, icha junok b'ab'el unin. Yelxo val ek'alto snivanil ol aj yelk'och vinh t'a yichanh masanil eb' rey.
Ol in xajanej vinh t'a junelnhej. Ha in trato yet' vinh, manh ol q'uexmajlaj.
Ha eb' yinhtilal vinh ol ak'an reyal sq'uexuloc, ol b'eynhejb'atoc yacb'an ayto ek' satcha’anh tik.
Palta tato ol yactejcan in k'ayb'ub'al eb' yinhtilal vinh chi', tato manh ol sk'anab'ajej eb' tas svala',
tato manh ol sb'eyb'alej in b'eyb'al eb', tato manh ol sk'anab'ajej in lolonel eb' svak' sk'ulej,
ol vak'och syaelal eb' yet' te' jixk'ab'te' yuj spital. Ol in mak' eb' yet' nok' tz'um yuj schucal.
Axo pax vinhaj David jun, manh ol vactejcan in xajanan vinh, ol vak'nhejelk'och in ti' ix vak' t'a vinh.
Manh ol ek'b'atlaj in trato yet' vinh. Ol vak'nhejelk'och tas ix valcan t'a vinh.
D'a junelnhej ix vak'kan in ti' t'a vinhaj David chi', a in ix vak' testigoal in b'a to manh ol in q'uexa'.
Ha eb' yinhtilal vinh ol ak'an reyal sq'uexuloc t'a vichanh t'a masanil tiempo icha yaj yoc k'u tik.
Tek'annhej ol ajek' eb' yak'an yajalil, icha yaj q'uen uj t'a satcha’anh, xa chi.
Axo ticnaic Mamin, ix a chaccanel vinh rey a sik'naccanelta, ix a patiquejcanel vinh. Ix cot oval t'a vinh.
Maj aq'uelk'och a trato t'a vinh a checab' chi'. Ix a yumcanel scorona vinh t'a sat lu'um.
Man jantacoc ix aj yolanil masanil smuroal schonhab' vinh. Ix ak' juvoquem schonhab' vinh.
Ha eb' anima tzek' ta', masanil tas ay t'a chonhab' chi', syelq'uejb'at eb'. Ha eb' ay t'a slak'anil vinh, sb'uchvaj eb' t'a vinh.
Ha ach ix ak' sk'ulej eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'a vinh, syik'anchaanh sk'ab' eb' yuj tzalajk'olal.
Ix iq'uel ye q'uen yespada vinh. Maj ach ochlaj yet' vinh ayic ix och oval.
Ix ak' lajvoc sb'inajnaquil vinh. Ix a yumancanem sdespacho vinh t'a sat lu'um.
Ix pet ichamax vinh uuj, niwan ix aj ak'an q'uixvelal vinh.
Mamin Jehová, ¿b'aq'uinh ol actej a k'ub'anel a b'a? ¿Ichanhej am tik ol ajcot yoval a k'ol icha junok oval k'ak'?
Mamin, nacoti to a co q'uinal tzapan toni. Ha onh anima onh tik, tzapan ix utejcan co q'uinal.
Malaj junok anima to malaj b'ak'uinh ol chamoc. Malaj mach syal scolan sb'ha t'a yol sk'ab' chamel.
Mamin, ¿b'ajtil ay a wach'k'olal a ch'oxnac t'a peca', aton ak'annac a ti' t'a vinhaj David, to ol ak' elk'och tas ix ala'?
Mamin, nacoti to manh jantacoc onh stzuntzan eb' anima a onh a checab' onh tik. Pitz'anoch tas tzonh yutej eb' chi' t'a in pixan.
Mamin Jehová, a eb' ayoch ajk'olal t'ayach tik, t'a junjun rato sb'uchvaj eb' t'a vinh a checab' sik'b'ilel uuj.
Alchajocab' wach' lolonel t'a Jehová t'a masanil tiempo. Ujocab'i.
